      "content": "i get the individualized approach, but i've heard some people talk about how certain groups perform better in specific sports, like sprinters vs endurance athletes. if there aren't biological differences, how do you explain the patterns we see in high-level athletics? like, is it all just environment and training, or is there some underlying physiological stuff people point to in scientific literature?",
